)ATTR DEFAULT(%+_)
)BODY Expand(//)
%Tutorial /-/  RJUST  /-/ Tutorial
%SELECTION ===>_ZCMD
%                     -------------------------------
                      О     Edit Macro  "RJUST"     О
                      -------------------------------
+
    This Edit Macro allows a user to right justify the data in a
    dataset against the right bounds. The only requirement is for the
    lines you wish modified to be marked by a о (cent) sign.


%SYNTAX:+   RJUST
+
+           There are no other operands for this command.
+           The lines you want modified must be designated with
+           the "о" sign. Use о followed by a number or a block
+           command version (оо оо).
+
)PROC
     &ZUP = #EMCH
)END
